cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.HC 

This paper is about crowdsourcing paraphrase generation, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning systems, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also analyzes the quality of the paraphrases generated by the crowd, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
